reviewText:
- capital shoots silent arrows of mass destruction;
- ogres and angry trees use teleportation cheats and conquer my 200+ turns empire in 10 turns;
- advisor tells me how to end a turn after 20 turns;
- sent some units through a flashy portal, next turn all units got obliterated;
- priest hero one-shots enemy forts;
- rogue mass invasions.

100% Recommend!

